data.text:
Thank You Fans, From The Walking Dead is a 12-minutes featurette special on AMC's The Walking Dead. It originally aired on November 24, 2022 on AMC. This was used as a way to honor the fans of The Walking Dead as the show was coming to an end.

Description[]

AMC & The Walking Dead want to thank The Walking Dead Family, The Best Fans in the World!
